`8Keywords``   : Spellsurge
`8Categories`` : 
`4++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++``

`8Syntax:`` 

 * sps 'spell' 'spell' spell' spell'

 This skill allows a spellcaster to cast up to 4 spells in rapid succession.
The amount of spells you may cast at once is dependent on your constitution.

